title: 1954 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 01)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
1954 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

When you go this far back in history, understandably there wasn't nearly as much Christian music being recorded as there is today.  And although I'm positive there were far more recorded than the four albums which I am sharing today, unfortunately only these four albums from 1954 ever have made their way into my collection over the years.  And in turn, into your collection today.

There are 4 albums being shared today, including...

 * Blackwood Brothers - 1954 - I'm Bound For That City
 * Blackwood Brothers - 1954 - Vintage Years
 * Eddy Arnold - 1954 - When It's Round Up Time In Heaven
 * George Lewis - 1954 - Jazz At Vespers

For Him,
TorrentTracts, May 2014
